Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.58,0:00:04.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 学校有什么新鲜事吗  - 没有\N{\fs38}- What's new at school? - Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.34,0:00:07.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有 呃 有个盛饭的阿姨死了\N{\fs38}Nothing! Oh, uh, one of the lunch ladies died.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.42,0:00:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在体育馆被发现的 脖子上有两个洞\N{\fs38}They found her in the gym with, like, two holes in her neck,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.73,0:00:10.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血被吸干了\N{\fs38}and all the blood drained out of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.98,0:00:12.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老天 谁能做出这种事情\N{\fs38}Good lord! Who does something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.00,0:00:15.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,显然是吸血鬼啊 胡椒呢\N{\fs38}Obviously a vampire. W-w-where's the pepper?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.53,0:00:17.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 吸血鬼真的存在吗\N{\fs38}Wait, what?! Vampires are real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.34,0:00:20.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是真的 谁知道呢\N{\fs38}Yes, Summer, vampires are real. Who knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.24,0:00:22.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦对 所有人都知道 几百年了都\N{\fs38}Oh, right, all humanity, for hundreds of years, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.76,0:00:24.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 宇宙之大 无奇不有\N{\fs38}Yeah, Summer, it's a big universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.42,0:00:26.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早点习惯吧 对吧 Rick\N{\fs38}Get used to it. R-right, Rick?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.52,0:00:27.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们要怎么办\N{\fs38}Well, what are we going to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.65,0:00:29.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直活着 到死为止\N{\fs38}We're gonna live our lives until we die.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.59,0:00:31.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能被吸血鬼吸干\N{\fs38}Possibly by vampire.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.01,0:00:33.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更可能被车撞扁 或者心脏病而死\N{\fs38}More likely auto accident or heart disease,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.03,0:00:34.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过也还是可能死于吸血鬼\N{\fs38}but possibly vampire.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.39,0:00:37.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外公 你能不能动用你超人的智慧\N{\fs38}Grandpa Rick, couldn't you, like, use your superknowledge
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.40,0:00:40.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成青少年混进我们学校\N{\fs38}to turn yourself into a teenager and come to our school
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.23,0:00:42.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我们抓住这只吸血鬼\N{\fs38}and help us hunt the vampire down?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.81,0:00:44.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 你这\N{\fs38}Um-- wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.31,0:00:46.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想得还挺详细\N{\fs38}Yeah, pretty specific pitch, Summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.75,0:00:49.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我兴许可以变成青少年\N{\fs38}I probably could turn myself into a teenager
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.63,0:00:52.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混进满是青春痘和荷尔蒙\N{\fs38}And hang out in the zit-covered, hormone-addled,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.04,0:00:54.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,低端垃圾横行的狗屁中学\N{\fs38}Low-stakes assworld that is high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.04,0:00:54.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs38\an8}Low-stakes testing在教育测试体系内是一种结果较为宽松 竞争压力小的评分系统
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.15,0:00:55.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我要反问一句\N{\fs38}But here's my reverse ask--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.82,0:00:58.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我[哔]为什么要这么做\N{\fs38}Why in the [bleep] would I ever do that, ever?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:01.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你凭什么要求我这么做\N{\fs38}And how dare you even ask me that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.47,0:01:03.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这样也算是恬不知耻了\N{\fs38}And why aren't you more ashamed of yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.60,0:01:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爸\N{\fs38}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.26,0:01:05.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要知耻 宝贝\N{\fs38}Be ashamed of yourself, sweetie.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:07.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jerry 你意识到你刚对女儿说了什么吗\N{\fs38}Jerry! Do you know what you just said to our daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.33,0:01:09.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 刚才我没在意\N{\fs38}Sor-ry! I wasn't paying attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.33,0:01:11.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在意关于吸血鬼的事情吗\N{\fs38}To a conversation about vampires?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.75,0:01:14.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很明显 我不知道是吸血鬼的事情\N{\fs38}Clearly, I didn't know it was about vampires,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.73,0:01:16.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我就没注意\N{\fs38}Because I wasn't paying attention,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.47,0:01:18.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是对我上点心\N{\fs38}Which you would know, if you ever
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.18,0:01:19.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就该知道我刚才没注意\N{\fs38}paid attention to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.56,0:01:21.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来了 这就进入受害者的角色了\N{\fs38}Oh, here we go, right to the victim role.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.48,0:01:22.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底是个受害者\N{\fs38}Am I a victim, Beth,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.68,0:01:25.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是娶了一个恶毒无比\N{\fs38}Or am I married to a mean, unfair monster
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.23,0:01:26.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还总是伤害我的魔鬼\N{\fs38}That always hurts me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.48,0:01:27.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老天爷\N{\fs38}Jesus christ!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.84,0:01:30.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们要是解决不了婚姻问题 赶紧离婚了事\N{\fs38}Will you fix your marriage or get a divorce already?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.10,0:01:35.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们试过一次婚姻咨询\N{\fs38}Well, we tried a couples' therapist.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.46,0:01:36.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是地球上的心理咨询\N{\fs38}That's earth therapy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.68,0:01:38.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就好比找一匹马来修旋转木马\N{\fs38}You might as well ask a horse to fix a merry-go-round.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.83,0:01:40.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它再怎么想努力\N{\fs38}I mean, he'll try his best, but mostly,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.53,0:01:41.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也只能被吓坏而已\N{\fs38}He's just gonna get horrified.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.75,0:01:44.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道外星球有一个百分百成功的地方\N{\fs38}I know about a place off-planet with a 100% success rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.32,0:01:47.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也想让婚姻继续啊 如果我们能的话\N{\fs38}Well, we want to make it work, if we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.51,0:01:48.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 但是  - 那就这么定了\N{\fs38}- It's just..  - Then it's settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.84,0:01:49.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用打包衣物了\N{\fs38}No need to pack.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.73,0:01:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出发出发出发\N{\fs38}Let's go, go, go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.87,0:01:55.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得老爸和老妈\N{\fs38}Do you think mom and dad are, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.22,0:01:56.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会离婚吗\N{\fs38}Gonna get a divorce?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.28,0:01:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么想想还是可以的\N{\fs38}I think it's okay to dream, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.26,0:02:00.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去做几根木钉\N{\fs38}I'm gonna go make some wooden stakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.74,0:02:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在婚四所给你们定了两天的强化治疗\N{\fs38}I booked you for a two-day intensive at Nuptia Four,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.45,0:02:39.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他家是银河系里最好的婚姻咨询机构\N{\fs38}The galaxy's most successful couples' counseling institute.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.38,0:02:40.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们甚至可以挽救\N{\fs38}They could save the marriage of a dog
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.83,0:02:42.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狗和巧克力的婚姻\N{\fs38}and a bar of dark chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.43,0:02:44.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个色情影星的婚姻\N{\fs38}They could save the marriage of a porn star and a porn star.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.82,0:02:47.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少我是愿意试一试的\N{\fs38}Well, I know I'm ready to try whatever it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.28,0:02:49.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这话是说我不愿意咯\N{\fs38}Which clearly implies that I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.34,0:02:50.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是要比什么 Beth\N{\fs38}It's not a competition, Beth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.74,0:02:52.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打赢嘴仗的策略就是\N{\fs38}Oh is that how you're gonna try to win,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.18,0:02:53.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗示说我太争强好胜是吧\N{\fs38}By implying I'm competitive?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.72,0:02:54.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你不是吗\N{\fs38}If the shoe fits.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.58,0:02:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 是你妈个头  - 呵呵\N{\fs38}- My shoe fits up your ass. - You wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.33,0:02:57.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们咨询愉快 周四见\N{\fs38}Okay, have fun. See ya Thursday!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.93,0:02:58.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼\N{\fs38}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.84,0:03:00.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这老混蛋\N{\fs38}Jerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.56,0:03:01.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么说我爸\N{\fs38}Don't insult my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.86,0:03:03.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了他的基因 我们的孩子才只是半蠢而不是全蠢\N{\fs38}He's the reason our kids are only half-stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.88,0:03:05.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈 你刚才说自己\N{\fs38}Ha! You just called yourself --
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.12,0:03:06.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂了\N{\fs38}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.66,0:03:08.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Smith夫妇吗  - 是的\N{\fs38}- Beth and Jerry Smith? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.45,0:03:09.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是Glaxo Slimslom\N{\fs38}I'm Glaxo Slimslom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.83,0:03:11.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎来到婚四所\N{\fs38}Welcome to Nuptia Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.71,0:03:14.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里能解决你们婚姻的烦恼\N{\fs38}Your marriage can rest easy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.86,0:03:18.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jerry 坐在这里 把这个戴上\N{\fs38}Jerry, go ahead and sit there and put this on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.40,0:03:21.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个仪器可以扫描提取你大脑中\N{\fs38}This machine isolates the part of the subject's brain
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.83,0:03:24.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于你对配偶的感知\N{\fs38}Containing all perceptions of its romantic partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.32,0:03:28.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在扫描Jerry对Beth的感知\N{\fs38}And we will now render Jerry's perception of Beth
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.27,0:03:31.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并具体化为人工生物的形象\N{\fs38}With artificial biological life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.16,0:03:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个有意思\N{\fs38}Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.00,0:03:38.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么玩意 收回你的想法\N{\fs38}What the hell is that?! Take that back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.08,0:03:39.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟然把我想成这样\N{\fs38}You do not think that about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.63,0:03:40.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么都没做啊\N{\fs38}I didn't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.88,0:03:42.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们把我的想法扫描出来了\N{\fs38}They scanned it out of my brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.30,0:03:43.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能收回那个想法吗\N{\fs38}Can I take it back?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.40,0:03:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么好后悔的\N{\fs38}There's nothing to regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.88,0:03:47.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就是要处理这些无意识 不健康的想法\N{\fs38}We're dealing with unconscious, unhealthy thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.16,0:03:48.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该你了\N{\fs38}Beth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.60,0:03:51.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在扫描Beth对Jerry的感知\N{\fs38}Now, we scan for Beth's perceptions of Jerry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.72,0:03:53.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使劲扫 他于我与死人无异\N{\fs38}Scan hard. He's dead to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.16,0:03:54.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么对你来说都是死物吧\N{\fs38}Everything's dead to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.28,0:03:54.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你再说一遍  - 没事\N{\fs38}- What? - Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.67,0:04:02.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好看看 一边哭去吧\N{\fs38}Read it and weep, bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.86,0:04:04.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都看到我是什么意思了吧\N{\fs38}Does everybody see what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.87,0:04:06.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个的意思 大家都看得很清楚\N{\fs38}I think we all see what you both mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.34,0:04:10.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吸血鬼的事有什么进展吗\N{\fs38}Any leads on the vampire?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.68,0:04:12.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样 我是说\N{\fs38}No, Summer! I mean, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.13,0:04:14.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就别再在意这事情了\N{\fs38}I think it might be time that we just l-let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.42,0:04:16.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得这没什么大不了\N{\fs38}Oh, so, now, you're too cool for this,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.24,0:04:17.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因为外公也这么想吗\N{\fs38}Just because grandpa Rick is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.49,0:04:19.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是因为这个 宇宙实在太大了\N{\fs38}It's not that, it's just that the universe
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.43,0:04:21.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没必要在意这么微不足道的事\N{\fs38}is a little too big to care about something so small.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.18,0:04:22.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊\N{\fs38}Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.62,0:04:24.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们好啊 小海辛们\N{\fs38}What up, my Helsings?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.62,0:04:24.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs38\an8}范海辛是著名的吸血鬼猎人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.12,0:04:26.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁想来猎杀吸血鬼 哈哈\N{\fs38}Who wants to hunt a vampire? Ha ha ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.54,0:04:27.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rick 你 你怎么\N{\fs38}Rick? How-- how did you--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.93,0:04:29.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚才无聊来着 然后想起来\N{\fs38}Yeah, I got bored and then, I remembered,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.18,0:04:31.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今早我回绝了Summer 然后我寻思\N{\fs38}This morning, how I blew Summer off, and I thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.18,0:04:33.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛非得跟个老混蛋似的\N{\fs38}Hey, why are you such a grumpy douche, Rick?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.19,0:04:34.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧到车库里\N{\fs38}Go to the garage,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.05,0:04:36.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把自己的思维传输到少年的克隆体\N{\fs38}transfer your mind into a younger clone of yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.22,0:04:38.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后加入到年轻人的狂欢里吧\N{\fs38}and get embroiled in some youthful hijinks,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.04,0:04:39.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么大不了的\N{\fs38}What's the BFD?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.28,0:04:40.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我就来了 我是小Rick\N{\fs38}So here I am. I'm tiny Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.98,0:04:42.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 好吧\N{\fs38}O-o-okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.25,0:04:43.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来了就好 Rick\N{\fs38}Well, it's good you're here, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.53,0:04:45.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们自己肯定搞不定\N{\fs38}I was pretty sure we didn't have what it takes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.09,0:04:46.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个吸血的东西的\N{\fs38}to deal with a bloodsucker on our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.63,0:04:48.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别妄自菲薄 Summer\N{\fs38}Don't short-sell yourself, Summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.13,0:04:50.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你完全能做到 但是我们[哔]组队的话\N{\fs38}You got everything it takes. But it'll still be fun
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.40,0:04:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是很有趣啊 小Rick[哔]无敌\N{\fs38}To do this as a [bleep] team, mother[bleep] tiny Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.88,0:04:55.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天呐 Toby Matthews来了\N{\fs38}Oh, my god, Toby Matthews!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.90,0:04:57.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨 我是小Rick 我新来的\N{\fs38}Hey, Toby. I'm tiny Rick. I'm new.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.73,0:05:00.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别欺负我哦 哈哈 开玩笑的\N{\fs38}Hey oh-- go easy on me. Ha ha. Just kiddin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.18,0:05:02.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就喜欢你这种直接的性格\N{\fs38}I like your straightforward style.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.83,0:05:04.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这实验服的行头挺酷的\N{\fs38}And that lab coat's pretty cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.10,0:05:06.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊Summer\N{\fs38}Summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.59,0:05:07.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他知道我的名字\N{\fs38}He knew my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.64,0:05:09.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他怎么会不知道 你长这么美\N{\fs38}Why wouldn't he? You're great!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.27,0:05:10.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我们还是小心为妙\N{\fs38}But, listen, just be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.63,0:05:12.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不能排除任何人是吸血鬼的嫌疑\N{\fs38}We can't rule anybody out as the vampire,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:14.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男神也不行\N{\fs38}Not even the dreamboats.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.52,0:05:15.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌\N{\fs38}Stop, tiny Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:18.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟孙子孙女杀吸血鬼去啦\N{\fs38}Huntin' a vampire with my grandkids!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.03,0:05:19.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小Rick[哔]无敌\N{\fs38}[bleep]tiny Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.80,0:05:22.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一步是观察你们的构造体\N{\fs38}The next step is to watch your mythologues
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.78,0:05:25.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,观察他们之间的互动 "意外"的是\N{\fs38}interact together and, uh-- big surprise--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.68,0:05:26.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,场面从来都不好看\N{\fs38}It's never pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.01,0:05:30.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是Gloompfschs夫妇\N{\fs38}Here we have Garrrh and Zharbidar Gloompfschs,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.51,0:05:32.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换种说法\N{\fs38}Or, should I say, here we have the way
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.61,0:05:35.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是这对夫妇对对方的感知\N{\fs38}Garrrh and Zharbidar perceive each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.60,0:05:38.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很明显\N{\fs38}As we can all see,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.78,0:05:40.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这根本不是他们本来的样子\N{\fs38}This is hardly the real Garrrh and Zharbidar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.93,0:05:42.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这很好 因为在他们脑海里\N{\fs38}Which is good, because the relationship
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.83,0:05:44.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们的婚姻关系不仅丑恶\N{\fs38}In their heads is not only ugly,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.24,0:05:46.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且难以维系\N{\fs38}It's unsustainable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.62,0:05:53.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们可能已经学到了重要的一课\N{\fs38}You may already be learning something important--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.72,0:05:55.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们看到的所有婚姻关系都各不相同\N{\fs38}All of these relationships are different,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.00,0:05:59.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不真实 而且没有一对能行的通\N{\fs38}None of them are real, and none of them work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.04,0:06:02.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们并不是对方时常认为的魔鬼模样\N{\fs38}We are not the monsters we sometimes see each other as,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.46,0:06:06.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们是真实的 我们是协调的\N{\fs38}Because we are real and we are functional.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.67,0:06:09.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因为此 我们比这些怪物好多了\N{\fs38}That's what makes us better than them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.96,0:06:11.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们能解决问题\N{\fs38}We can find solutions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.20,0:06:13.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能相互适应\N{\fs38}We can adapt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.86,0:06:15.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能相互交流\N{\fs38}We can communicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.17,0:06:18.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最重要的是\N{\fs38}And, most importantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.22,0:06:23.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们能相互合作\N{\fs38}We can work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.12,0:06:27.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然颇有坎坷 最后终于苦尽甘来\N{\fs38}Well, it was a tough adventure, but it paid off --
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.48,0:06:29.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学校里没有吸血鬼啦\N{\fs38}Our school is vampire-free!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:32.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到Feratu教练竟然是吸血鬼\N{\fs38}Man, who would've suspected coach Feratu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:32.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs38\an8}这个名字出自著名的吸血鬼诺斯费拉图
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.03,0:06:33.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们做得很好 功不可没\N{\fs38}You did great, guys. Couldn't have done it without ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.96,0:06:35.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要为自己感到骄傲\N{\fs38}You know, we-- w-we should be proud of ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.89,0:06:38.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们杀了一个吸血鬼 同时干掉一个体育老师\N{\fs38}We killed a vampire and a gym teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.10,0:06:40.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈 也算一石二鸟\N{\fs38}Ha ha ha. Talk about two-for-one, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.25,0:06:42.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你原本的身体是\N{\fs38}So, how, exactly, is your old body
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.17,0:06:43.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么在这里面维持生命的啊\N{\fs38}living in there, grandpa Rick?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.64,0:06:45.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是高压氧量子液体\N{\fs38}Oh, you know, hyperbaric quantum fluid,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.58,0:06:46.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乱七八糟的东西\N{\fs38}That kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.70,0:06:48.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以保存生物组织\N{\fs38}It preserves living tissue.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:49.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没多少东西要保存的了\N{\fs38}Not that there was much to preserve.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.56,0:06:51.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看那皮包骨跟木乃伊似的\N{\fs38}Look at that mummy! Ha! Ha ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.68,0:06:54.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我该回到那老家伙的身体里了\N{\fs38}And I guess it's time for me to get back inside the old-timer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:06:58.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天呐Toby Matthews问我父母在不在家\N{\fs38}Oh, my god. Toby Matthews is asking if my parents
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.46,0:07:00.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还问我能不能开派对\N{\fs38}Are still out of town and if we can have a party!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.21,0:07:02.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真棒 Summer 你看我上午说什么来着\N{\fs38}All right, way to go, Summer! What did I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.88,0:07:05.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他还问小Rick会不会来\N{\fs38}Ohh! He's asking if tiny Rick will be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.94,0:07:07.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Summer 我转念一想\N{\fs38}Well, you know what, Summer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.16,0:07:09.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你告诉他 小Rick会过去的\N{\fs38}Tell him tiny Rick will be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.22,0:07:10.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他带点酒来\N{\fs38}And tell him to bring some brews!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.78,0:07:13.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗 你 你会以小Rick的身份留下\N{\fs38}For real? Y-y-y-you would stay as tiny Rick,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.50,0:07:13.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就为了留下来开派对\N{\fs38}Just so we can have a party?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:16.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 多一晚又有什么关系\N{\fs38}Hell, yeah! What's one more night?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.74,0:07:19.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说这老家伙在这儿 谁能尽兴啊\N{\fs38}And who can have fun with this old bastard hanging around, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.10,0:07:21.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wubby lubby doob doob\N{\fs38}Wubby lubby doob doob!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.38,0:07:23.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小Rick\N{\fs38}Tiny Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.54,0:07:28.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来 这边是Beth和Jerry Smith\N{\fs38}Moving on. Now, we have beth and jerry smith
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:30.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来自地一球行星\N{\fs38}From the planet e-arth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.54,0:07:31.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心跳得很厉害\N{\fs38}My heart is pounding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.55,0:07:32.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会很棒\N{\fs38}This is gonna be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.56,0:07:34.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地一球的两性关系比较简单\N{\fs38}The e-arth relationships are simpler.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.64,0:07:37.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是一个原始星球 所以他们的失调状态\N{\fs38}It's a primitive planet, so their dysfunctions are oh --
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.30,0:07:39.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 发生了什么\N{\fs38}W-wait, what? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.36,0:07:40.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Smith夫妇的构造体在哪\N{\fs38}Where are the smith mythologues?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.00,0:07:47.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的天啊\N{\fs38}Oh, my god.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.52,0:07:52.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 天啊  - 守住那个牢房\N{\fs38}- Oh, my god. - Secure the cell!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.28,0:07:57.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁想参观一下礼品店 很有趣的\N{\fs38}Uh, hey! You know what's fun? Our gift shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:07:59.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们何不有序地前往\N{\fs38}Why don't we proceed in an orderly --
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.58,0:08:03.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的老天\N{\fs38}Oh, dear god, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.78,0:08:05.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是互利共生的\N{\fs38}They're codependent!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.65,0:08:06.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑\N{\fs38}Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.76,0:08:17.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的 你真的很会驾驭\N{\fs38}Oh, yeah, yeah, you really know how to
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.92,0:08:19.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 蓝色的衣服啊  - 真的吗\N{\fs38}- sport that color blue. - Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.68,0:08:21.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你今天真的很美  - 我的天啊 \N{\fs38}- You're looking real good. - Oh, my god.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:24.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你好 Morty  - 你好啊 Jessica\N{\fs38}- Hey, morty. Oh, hey - hey, Jessica.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.26,0:08:27.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 小Rick是你的亲兄弟还是表的\N{\fs38}So, is tiny Rick your brother or cousin, or...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.91,0:08:29.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不是 我外公把他的意识\N{\fs38}No, my grandpa just transferred
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.46,0:08:31.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转移到他自己的克隆体上了\N{\fs38}His consciousness into a clone of himself
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.18,0:08:32.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样他就可以来我们学校了\N{\fs38}So he could be in our high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.52,0:08:33.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帅气\N{\fs38}Cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:35.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快来看 小Rick在弹吉他\N{\fs38}Hey, tiny Rick's playing guitar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.68,0:08:36.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位朋友\N{\fs38}All right, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.78,0:08:38.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一首来自我的内心\N{\fs38}This next one's coming straight from the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.40,0:08:40.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想到哪儿唱到哪儿 现场发挥的歌词\N{\fs38}Making the lyrics up right off the top of my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.04,0:08:43.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*放我出来 你所见的*\N{\fs38}*Let me out, What you see*
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.32,0:08:45.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*只是一个假的驱壳*\N{\fs38}*is not the  same person as me*
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.40,0:08:48.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*我的生活是个谎言 我不是你望着的那个人*\N{\fs38}*My life's a lie, I'm not who you're looking at*
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.38,0:08:51.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*放我出来 给我自由 我已年迈*\N{\fs38}*Let me out, set me free,I'm really old *
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.24,0:08:52.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*这不是真正的我*\N{\fs38}*This isn't me*
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.30,0:08:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*我的身体在大缸里渐渐死亡*\N{\fs38}*My real body's slowly dying in a vat*
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:09:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*有人听到我的呐喊吗 有人明白我吗*\N{\fs38}*Is anybody listening, can anyone understand*
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.54,0:09:04.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*别再傻盯着我了 救救我吧*\N{\fs38}*Stop Looking at me like that and actually help me*
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.00,0:09:07.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*救我 救救我 我要死了*\N{\fs38}*Help! Help me, I'm gonna die*
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.10,0:09:09.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是小Rick 谢谢捧场\N{\fs38}Tiny Rick! Thanks, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.70,0:09:10.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙太赞了\N{\fs38}This guy's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.95,0:09:12.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我爱小Rick   - 帅飞了\N{\fs38}- I love tiny Rick! - Bad ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.97,0:09:36.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么[哔]\N{\fs38}What the [bleep]?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.38,0:09:38.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是 你们这机构怎么搞的\N{\fs38}Yeah, I know! What kind of operation are you running?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.94,0:09:41.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们 你们两夫妇是什么的婚姻关系啊\N{\fs38}Us?! What the hell kind of relationship do you have?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.84,0:09:43.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好 怪在我们的头上\N{\fs38}Oh, right, blame this on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.20,0:09:46.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 没错 我就怪在你们头上\N{\fs38}Okay, uh, I can and I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.40,0:09:49.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的恶魔化构造体居然在合作\N{\fs38}Your demonized mythologizations of each other are cooperating.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.82,0:09:50.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是好事吗\N{\fs38}Isn't that good?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.06,0:09:53.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是 糟透了\N{\fs38}No. No! It's bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.46,0:09:56.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的婚姻是我见过最糟的\N{\fs38}You have the single worst marriage I've ever witnessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.76,0:09:57.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不应该存在\N{\fs38}It shouldn't exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.80,0:10:00.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们根本完全彻底不应该在一起\N{\fs38}You should never, ever, ever, have gotten together
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.56,0:10:02.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还很不懂你们是怎么以及为什么\N{\fs38}And I do not understand how, or why,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.98,0:10:05.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会走到一起\N{\fs38}You would ever stay together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.58,0:10:08.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这婚姻咨询也太烂了吧\N{\fs38}Well, this is just bad couples' therapy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.18,0:10:09.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不是嘛\N{\fs38}Totally.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.23,0:10:15.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我们\N{\fs38}Wait for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.97,0:10:17.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,位置只够再多一人了\N{\fs38}There's only room for one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.51,0:10:19.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是心理咨询师 我跟他们说说\N{\fs38}I'm a therapist. I'll talk to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.25,0:10:21.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们不是咨询师 马上走\N{\fs38}They're not therapists. Go, go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.35,0:10:23.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定有办法联系上爸爸的\N{\fs38}There's gotta be a way to contact my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.05,0:10:25.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们找个控制室什么的\N{\fs38}Let's find a control room or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.87,0:10:33.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Beth 快来看看\N{\fs38}Beth! You'll want to see this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.57,0:10:34.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么\N{\fs38}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.33,0:10:35.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是个小型可拆卸面板\N{\fs38}It's a small, hinged panel
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.93,0:10:38.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后面有一些空间\N{\fs38}With a tiny amount of space behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.43,0:10:40.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你也能找到一个\N{\fs38}If you can find one, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.67,0:10:43.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来几个小时或几天我们就安全了\N{\fs38}We should be safe for hours, maybe days!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.23,0:10:46.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jerry 你在这里待好\N{\fs38}You stay put, Jerry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.45,0:10:47.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去求救 假如我能活着的话\N{\fs38}I'll send help, if I make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.95,0:10:50.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不找个地方自己躲起来吗\N{\fs38}You don't want to find your own little hatch?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.41,0:10:53.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jerry 我相信你独自躲好的话\N{\fs38}Jerry, I believe that, if you hide by yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.47,0:10:55.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以活下去\N{\fs38}You might survive and I believe I,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.73,0:10:57.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时我也相信 我独自也能逃出这里\N{\fs38}By myself, have a shot of getting out of here,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.99,0:11:00.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我们两人一起\N{\fs38}But the two of us, together?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.87,0:11:02.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fs38}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.27,0:11:03.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能那个心理医生是对的\N{\fs38}Look, maybe the shrink was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.59,0:11:05.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你好运\N{\fs38}Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.13,0:11:10.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我听好了\N{\fs38}All right, now, you listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.53,0:11:11.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实不听也可以\N{\fs38}Oh! Or don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.75,0:11:13.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别 求你了\N{\fs38}Hey! Don't! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.61,0:11:18.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊 别过来\N{\fs38}Oh, god, oh, god, oh, god!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.45,0:11:20.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白我以前说过什么\N{\fs38}Now, I know I've said, in the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.09,0:11:22.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,数学很重要 确实是\N{\fs38}That math is important -- and it is! --
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.13,0:11:24.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还认为 总有一天 你们会回想起\N{\fs38}But I also think that, one day, you'll all look back
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.75,0:11:28.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟小Rick和Morty做同学的日子\N{\fs38}On being in high school with tiny Rick and Morty,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.32,0:11:31.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为听说他们昨晚搞了一个超级棒的派对\N{\fs38}Who I hear had a great party last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.27,0:11:33.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 下课\N{\fs38}So, class dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.29,0:11:34.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天放你们假\N{\fs38}You've got the day off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.53,0:11:36.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干的好 Goldenfold先生\N{\fs38}All right! Good work, mr. Goldenfold!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.70,0:11:38.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 到外面转转 多读书\N{\fs38}Yeah, get outside. Read a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.77,0:11:40.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Danielle 涂点防晒霜\N{\fs38}Put on some sunscreen, Danielle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.33,0:11:42.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Summer 你好 上衣真漂亮\N{\fs38}Hey, what's up, Summer? Ooh, nice top.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.33,0:11:44.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 小Rick 你觉得\N{\fs38}Thanks. Tiny rick, you think you might be
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.15,0:11:45.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你今晚可以回到老的身体里去吗\N{\fs38}Getting back into your old body tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.87,0:11:47.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行喔 今晚是舞会之夜\N{\fs38}No can do. Tonight's the big dance
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.94,0:11:50.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty还会带Jessica出席 他需要这架小僚机\N{\fs38}And Morty's bringing Jessica. He needs his tiny wing man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.45,0:11:52.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小Rick\N{\fs38}Tiny Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.23,0:11:54.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚不行的话要等到什么时候\N{\fs38}Okay, but if not tonight, when?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.77,0:11:56.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不清楚 等我想回去了\N{\fs38}I don't know. When I feel like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.45,0:11:58.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你别这么咄咄逼人的\N{\fs38}Damn, girl! You need to chill out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.72,0:12:00.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事是你先想出来的\N{\fs38}This whole thing was your idea, in the first place,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.72,0:12:02.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在又是你想尽快结束\N{\fs38}And, now, you're trying to rush it along.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.51,0:12:04.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不是嘛 我喜欢高中\N{\fs38}Yeah, and you know what? I like high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.03,0:12:05.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢跟大家玩 小Rick万岁\N{\fs38}I like hanging out. Tiny rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.76,0:12:08.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果喜欢这样生活的人不是真正的你呢\N{\fs38}But what if the you that likes it isn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.13,0:12:12.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别傻了 Summer\N{\fs38}Oh, Summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.57,0:12:14.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是有个年轻驱壳的Rick\N{\fs38}It's just Rick in a younger body.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.03,0:12:15.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会 会 会 会\N{\fs38}What's the -- what's -- what's -- what's --
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.27,0:12:16.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会有什么问题啊\N{\fs38}What's the -- what's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.81,0:12:18.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看他的画 Morty\N{\fs38}Look at his art, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.49,0:12:19.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最近走情绪摇滚风\N{\fs38}I've got an emo streak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.83,0:12:21.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也算是我这么酷炫的部分原因\N{\fs38}It's part of what makes me so rad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.14,0:12:23.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这里写着"救救我 Morty和Summer"\N{\fs38}Why does it say "Help me morty and summer!"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.39,0:12:26.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Summer 这是画的题目\N{\fs38}Come on, Summer, that's the title of the art.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.59,0:12:28.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么<霹雳游侠>叫霹雳游侠\N{\fs38}Why was knight rider called knight rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.59,0:12:28.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs38\an8}<霹雳游侠> 80年代电视剧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.33,0:12:30.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,车的名字明明是Kitt 被人开的不是Michael Knight.\N{\fs38}The car's name was kitt. Nobody rode Michael Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.33,0:12:30.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs38\an8}男主名叫Michael Knight
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.83,0:12:33.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想多了 Summer 我是小Rick\N{\fs38}You're overthinking it, summer. I'm tiny rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.33,0:12:35.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外公 我觉得 你把意识\N{\fs38}Grandpa, I think that, when you put your mind
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.75,0:12:37.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放进这个年轻的躯体了\N{\fs38}Into this body's young brain,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.13,0:12:38.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就做年轻人做的事\N{\fs38}It did what young brains do --
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.59,0:12:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这副躯体把坏的想法压在心底\N{\fs38}It shoved the bad thoughts into the back
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.73,0:12:42.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掩藏起来\N{\fs38}And put a wall around them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.45,0:12:44.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那些想法属于真正的Rick\N{\fs38}But those bad thoughts are the real Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.95,0:12:46.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经年迈的事实\N{\fs38}The fact that you're old, the fact that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.71,0:12:48.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们终有一天会死的事实\N{\fs38}We're all going to die, one day, the fact that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.37,0:12:50.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙很大 任何事都很渺小的事实\N{\fs38}The universe is so big, nothing in it matters,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.65,0:12:52.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些事实才造就真正的你\N{\fs38}Those facts are who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.53,0:12:54.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以真正的Rick被困住了\N{\fs38}So you're trapped in there and you can only
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.29,0:12:57.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只能通过小Rick的青少年焦虑表现出来\N{\fs38}Come out in the form of tiny rick's teen angst!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.77,0:12:59.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Summer 我听说\N{\fs38}Well, Summer, I hear
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.55,0:13:02.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Toby Matthews 不喜欢神经兮兮瞎分析的女孩\N{\fs38}Toby Matthews isn't into psycho chicks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.11,0:13:03.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有人喜欢这类女孩\N{\fs38}Can't think of anyone that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.71,0:13:06.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舞会上见啦 兔崽子们 小Rick万岁\N{\fs38}I'll see you mother at the dance! Tiny rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.37,0:13:07.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty 你要帮我\N{\fs38}Morty, you have to help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.89,0:13:10.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Summer 他很开心 我也很开心 \N{\fs38}Summer, he's happy! I'm happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.27,0:13:11.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是你的目的吗\N{\fs38}I-I-is that why you're doing this,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.89,0:13:13.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不让我们开心\N{\fs38}You don't want me and rick to be happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.41,0:13:14.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是\N{\fs38}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.23,0:13:15.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就把你这些逼事儿收拾收拾\N{\fs38}Well, then get your shit together!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.71,0:13:18.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全收起来放到书包里\N{\fs38}Get it all together and put it in a backpack.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.35,0:13:20.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的逼事儿 好好收拾收拾\N{\fs38}All your shit, so it's together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.93,0:13:23.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你想把它们带走\N{\fs38}And if you gotta take it somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.47,0:13:24.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就快带走 懂吗\N{\fs38}Take it somewhere, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.75,0:13:26.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带到逼事儿店卖了\N{\fs38}Take it to the shit store and sell it
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.29,0:13:28.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者在逼事儿博物馆展览 我不管\N{\fs38}O-or put it in a shit museum. I don't care what you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.83,0:13:30.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 收拾好你的破逼事儿\N{\fs38}You just gotta get it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.66,0:13:33.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收拾好\N{\fs38}Get your shit together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.79,0:13:41.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别过来\N{\fs38}Get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.73,0:13:42.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 不是吧\N{\fs38}Wait, for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.43,0:13:46.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是Beth对我的看法\N{\fs38}You're how Beth sees me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.65,0:13:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fs38}Oh, my god.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.71,0:13:49.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转过身去\N{\fs38}Turn around!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.99,0:13:51.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说转过身去\N{\fs38}I said turn around!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.55,0:13:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Beth怎么会这样想我\N{\fs38}How can beth have these thoughts about me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.01,0:13:56.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个狗眼看人低的贱人\N{\fs38}That judgmental monster bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.71,0:13:57.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不接受\N{\fs38}I'm not taking this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.94,0:13:59.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想知道我的妻子在哪\N{\fs38}I want to know where my wife is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.43,0:14:01.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要协助我\N{\fs38}You are going to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.83,0:14:03.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停 别再这样了\N{\fs38}No! Nobody's doing that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.79,0:14:08.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别动\N{\fs38}Stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.91,0:14:09.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想干嘛\N{\fs38}What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.91,0:14:11.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更多Jerry\N{\fs38}Jerrys.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.23,0:14:13.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想要Jerry\N{\fs38}You want jerry?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.25,0:14:14.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都不想要Jerry\N{\fs38}I don't even want jerry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.75,0:14:17.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要很多Jerry\N{\fs38}I want Jerrys.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.87,0:14:20.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一支Jerry军队\N{\fs38}An army.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.49,0:14:23.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jerry军队\N{\fs38}An army of jerrys.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.11,0:14:26.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的顺从的价值都浪费在你身上了\N{\fs38}The value of his subservience is wasted on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.73,0:14:29.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要利用它来征服宇宙\N{\fs38}I will use it to dominate the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.03,0:14:31.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊 Jerry肯定觉得\N{\fs38}Ah ha ha. Boy, Jerry must think
