Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.65,0:15:44.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小Rick 我来找你谈话\N{\fs38}Tiny rick, this conversation
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.57,0:15:46.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我心碎得一片一片的\N{\fs38}Is gonna break my heart wide open.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.15,0:15:47.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是个很棒的学生 而且你是个\N{\fs38}You're a great student and the fact that
