Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.83,0:16:36.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Summer 我还以为你很酷呢\N{\fs38}Summer, I thought you were cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.35,0:16:37.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很抱歉 好么\N{\fs38}I'm sorry, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.97,0:16:39.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么可以这么婊啊\N{\fs38}How can you be such a bitch?
