Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.27,0:16:46.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,论什么叫自毁\N{\fs38}Talk about self-destructive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.23,0:16:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs38}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.33,0:16:51.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 那边那个Jerry迷\N{\fs38}Hey, jerry-lover!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.27,0:16:53.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要尝尝本尊的厉害\N{\fs38}How about a taste of the real thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.35,0:16:55.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jerry\N{\fs38}Jerry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.07,0:17:03.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有我在你就别想得逞\N{\fs38}Not on my watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.63,0:17:06.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了\N{\fs38}That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.93,0:17:09.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Beth 是我 你的丈夫\N{\fs38}Beth, it's me, your husband!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.57,0:17:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来救你了\N{\fs38}I'm here to save you.
