Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.49,0:17:44.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道么 你你你还不如变老吧\N{\fs38}You know, y-y-you may as well be old again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.49,0:17:45.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得你特厉害 是吧 Morty \N{\fs38}You think you're tough, huh, Morty?
