Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.53,0:17:49.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是你们学校最酷的学生\N{\fs38}I'm the coolest kid in your school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.35,0:17:51.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么让我对你言听计从啊 \N{\fs38}How are you gonna just make me do whatever you say, huh?
