Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.11,0:18:14.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要\N{\fs38}Ugh! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.33,0:18:15.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感受他的感受\N{\fs38}Feel what he's feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.75,0:18:18.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 天呐\N{\fs38}Ugh! Noooooooo! God!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.90,0:18:22.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦天呐 生命是什么\N{\fs38}Oh, God, what is life?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.53,0:18:25.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此有才华的人为何英年早逝\N{\fs38}How can someone so talented die so young
