Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.83,0:18:34.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真Rick\N{\fs38}Regular Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.75,0:18:36.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rick 我们怎么把你放回你的身体里\N{\fs38}Rick! How do we get you back into your body?
