Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.03,0:19:15.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是咱们的Beth\N{\fs38}Good old beth!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.97,0:19:18.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷如机器 毒如蛇蝎\N{\fs38}The mind of a robot and the heart of an insect!
