Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.47,0:20:12.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢了孩子们 你们解决了问题\N{\fs38}Thanks, kids. You figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.29,0:20:13.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  其实是Summer解决的\N{\fs38}Well, summer did.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.85,0:20:15.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是挺怪的 Morty你能那么愿意为了个妞\N{\fs38}Kind of weird that you were that willing
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.51,0:20:17.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我的整个存在给卖了\N{\fs38}To sell my existence out for some trim, Morty.
