Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.49,0:20:20.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是听着 我原谅你们俩 知道为什么不\N{\fs38}But listen— I forgive you both because you know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.79,0:20:22.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天学到了重要的东西\N{\fs38}I learned, today, something important—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.65,0:20:24.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青少年的心就是它自己最大的敌人\N{\fs38}The teenage mind is its own worst enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.85,0:20:26.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 我还学到了\N{\fs38}Oh, I also learned this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.39,0:20:31.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凤凰计划根本不可靠 不像我想的那样\N{\fs38}Operation phoenix is not the fallback I thought it would be.
