Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.63,0:20:34.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦天呐\N{\fs38}Oh, my god!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.25,0:20:38.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦我的天呐 穿裤子去\N{\fs38}Oh, my god. Put some pants on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.12,0:20:39.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿裤子\N{\fs38}Put pants on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.37,0:20:41.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外公回来了 宝贝\N{\fs38}Grandpa's back, baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.29,0:20:42.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外公\N{\fs38}Grandpa's --
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.89,0:20:44.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 我还得去接你们的爸妈\N{\fs38}Oh, man, I gotta pick up your parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.75,0:20:46.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他俩快把我电话打爆了\N{\fs38}They have been blowin' me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.69,0:20:48.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走前再砍一刀\N{\fs38}One last swing for the road!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.13,0:20:50.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的天呐 穿点衣服行么\N{\fs38}For the love of god, get dressed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.45,0:20:55.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说 你怎么想的 你想\N{\fs38}So, what do you think? You wanna
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.69,0:20:57.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咱俩再维持这段婚姻一段时间不\N{\fs38}Keep this marriage going a while longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.47,0:21:01.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少也得坚持到Morty高中毕业呀\N{\fs38}At least until morty has graduated high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.14,0:21:02.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 嗯\N{\fs38}Oh. Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.61,0:21:07.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊哈 你看 我怎么说的来着\N{\fs38}Aha, you see? What did I tell you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.07,0:21:07.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有效果吧\N{\fs38}It worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.87,0:21:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道么Rick 我想 从某种程度上来讲 可能\N{\fs38}You know what, rick? I guess, in a way, maybe—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.05,0:21:11.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没兴趣 上车\N{\fs38}Already lost interest. Get in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.82,0:21:13.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一整天都待在一个孩子的体内 \N{\fs38}I've been inside a kid all day and, now,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.37,0:21:15.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在都能听到我骨头相互摩擦的声音\N{\fs38}I can feel my bones scraping each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.03,0:21:17.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你有点心理准备\N{\fs38}Uh, just so you're prepared,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.58,0:21:19.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,车库里有一堆我的尸体\N{\fs38}There's a bunch of dead mes in the garage.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.33,0:21:23.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈 听起来咱们的故事有一个共通的主题了\N{\fs38}Huh! Sounds like our stories were connected by a theme.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.31,0:21:25.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能 Jerry\N{\fs38}Not really, jerry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.19,0:21:28.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有可能就是表面上的联系而你的脑子觉得这是主题上的联系\N{\fs38}Probably a cosmetic connection your mind mistakes for thematic.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.93,0:21:29.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦\N{\fs38}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.72,0:21:31.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老Rick  毁掉一切\N{\fs38}Old rick! Ruinin' everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.21,0:22:08.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人\N{\fs38}Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.07,0:22:09.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说\N{\fs38}Speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.27,0:22:10.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Feratu教练的真身\N{\fs38}Coach Feratu's presence
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.71,0:22:12.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被人类识破了\N{\fs38}Was discovered by the humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.33,0:22:13.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他被杀掉了\N{\fs38}He has been destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.71,0:22:14.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事\N{\fs38}No bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.77,0:22:16.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凡人们很快就会\N{\fs38}The mortals shall soon—
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.17,0:22:17.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 你说谁来着\N{\fs38}I'm sorry, what did you say his name was?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.47,0:22:19.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Feratu教练  - Feratu教练\N{\fs38}- Coach Feratu.  - Coach Feratu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.35,0:22:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是他的真名么 他的吸血鬼真名\N{\fs38}That was his real name, like his actual vampire name?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.69,0:22:24.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不不不 他的吸血鬼命叫Balik Alistane\N{\fs38}No no no no. His vampire name was balik alistane.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.41,0:22:25.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他怎么[哔]给自己起这么个名啊\N{\fs38}Why the [beep] would he name himself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.56,0:22:27.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟那么有名的吸血鬼电影一样的 他演什么戏呢\N{\fs38}after a famous vampire movie? Was he doing a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.69,0:22:29.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道 我不洁的主人\N{\fs38}I do not know, your unholiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.07,0:22:30.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耶稣[哔]基督啊\N{\fs38}Jesus [beep] Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.45,0:22:33.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从现在开始不许再有这些自以为机智乱起名的破事\N{\fs38}From now on, no more of this clever-name bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.13,0:22:34.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吸血鬼假装人类的时候\N{\fs38}When a vampire is pretending to be a human,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.81,0:22:35.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们只能给自己起像什么\N{\fs38}They can just call themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.95,0:22:37.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Alan Jefferson之类的名\N{\fs38}Alan Jefferson or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.05,0:22:39.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真有病 是不是\N{\fs38}It's crazy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.21,0:22:40.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说 我这么做很混蛋么\N{\fs38}I mean, am I being an asshole?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.57,0:22:42.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 我觉得屋里每一个人\N{\fs38}Okay, I feel like everybody in the room
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.24,0:22:43.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都跟看着个扫兴鬼 一样看着我\N{\fs38}Is looking at me like I'm the buzzkill.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.67,0:22:44.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是\N{\fs38}I'm not?
